{"tid":463104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"違反財政處理程序　林淳軒被革常委職務　退出香港眾志","createTime":"2017-11-09T07:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T08:59:48.000Z","uid":51904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"35800cfa157ce7cb718f8ae6d6fc4141539d96de","tid":463104,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:47:11.000Z","msg":"香港眾志發表聲明，指成員林淳軒違反黨內財政處理程序，經黨內調查後，裁定林淳軒違反黨員之行為操守，即時免去常委職務。聲明中指，香港眾志經確認並無財政損失。林淳軒已提出退黨申請並獲得批淮。<br />\n<br />\n林淳軒隨即在個人facebook上轉載香港眾志聲明，表示「對於眾志，實在有太多的抱歉和感謝」，又指今天是新旅程的開始，要繼續加油。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言表示驚訝和意外，又指希望香港眾志能詳細說明情況。另有網民留言表示，林淳軒應解釋清楚。"},{"pid":"ecbffeb796e8344c045459fe3c430b29017bc64d","tid":463104,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e64eabce59aa2c6e4ceae21fec0c94615e45d3","tid":463104,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35db7c56ef5f29b787852fb9d66dfaf58aef8b02","tid":463104,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"挪用公款孖閱文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5366855c6c7b053a8e38cb20379528fe68abe0d","tid":463104,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"乜佢地有財政處理程序咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d512318d2cb798bcc914ee91cb1d301366dfd7","tid":463104,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>挪用公款孖閱文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded9fda3e90183463bdafec4a1019b2eaf78c9f1","tid":463104,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"<